 who were slightly younger than me, who were doing the same kind of thing. Up till then, going to {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname country-region}}{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname PlaceName}}{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}Italy{\*\xmlclose}
