\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \b\insrsid10361243\charrsid15550915 Karen:\tab }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10361243\charrsid15550915 But when you went to this conference, in {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname City}}{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname 
PlaceName}}{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}Bologna{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose}, you were already doing some work with oral history?
