\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \b\insrsid5059545\charrsid15550915 Paul:\tab }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10361243\charrsid15550915 Yes, they copied and then edited. But then we had a problem
 with somebody from the BBC, who came and copied material without our permission, and after that I stopped them using it, because I just felt it was impossible with an unsupervised archive. And one of the advantages of the fact that it's now in the Britis
h Library National Sound Archive, is that it can be used in a proper way by radio people, and I'm sure, in the long-run, it will be used rather a lot.
