\par }\pard \ltrpar\s20\qj \li1871\ri0\widctlpar\wrapdefault\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin1871\itap0\pararsid5536854 {\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10361243\charrsid15550915 Then I did the research on {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname 
country-region}}{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname PlaceName}}{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}Scotland{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose}, and I did most of the interviews there, [for }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
