\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \b\insrsid10361243\charrsid15550915 Karen:\tab }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10361243\charrsid15550915 How many interviews did you do?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \b\insrsid5536854\charrsid15550915 Paul:\tab }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10361243\charrsid15550915 
Well, for that project, there's [around 150, and I did about] a hundred altogether. Two or three hundred hours, maybe.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \b\insrsid10361243\charrsid15550915 Karen:\tab }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10361243\charrsid15550915 Each interview would be like three hours or two?
