\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \b\insrsid10361243\charrsid15550915 Karen:\tab }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10361243\charrsid15550915 So how did you [write it up]? You were listening?
