\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \b\insrsid10361243\charrsid15550915 Karen:\tab }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10361243\charrsid15550915 But you read the whole interview? You don't, for instance, just read through the part that the person is j
ust talking about a theme, say] religion, funerals, about death?
