\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \b\insrsid8224390\charrsid15550915 Paul:\tab }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10361243\charrsid15550915 Yes, }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \i\insrsid10361243\charrsid15550915 Living With Fishing}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
