o is a child and adolescent psychiatrist, and who has also a clinical perspective, but a somewhat different one, because she's medically-trained, and I think also, although she's been very interested in family therapy, she's also practised in other therap
ies with families, and more straight medical ones. So that we had a series of approaches. 
